{"id":1678151,"retrievedAt":"2026-04-22T12:19:07.271Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/mqHCv5cbpIHso5B5D3Os9P8N9k5.jpg","belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":99,"name":"Documentary"}],"homepage":"","id":1678151,"imdb_id":"tt37062073","origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"de","original_title":"Croatias Coast - Endless and Wild","overview":"For millions of Central Europeans, the Croatian coast is a place of longing, a popular travel destination with Mediterranean flair. But away from the beaches, a world begins that often remains hidden to us humans: Over 1,000 islands, more than 6,000 kilometers of coastline - a habitat between land and sea that not only offers scenic diversity, but also plenty of space for animal inhabitants. The new \"Universum\" documentary \"Croatia's Coast - Endless and Wild\" by Marc Graf and Christine Sonvilla takes us into familiar, but also little-known natural areas. With impressive images, the film awakens the desire to travel and opens up a view of a fascinatingly wild coast that is far more than just a vacation paradise.","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":null,"production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2025-05-27","revenue":0,"runtime":52,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"German","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"For millions of Central Europeans, the Croatian coast is a place of longing, a popular travel destination with Mediterranean flair. But away from the beaches, a world begins that often remains hidden to us humans","title":"Croatias Coast - Endless and Wild","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[{"iso_3166_1":"DE","title":"Kroatiens Küste - Endlos und wild","type":""},{"iso_3166_1":"AU","title":"Croatias Coast","type":""},{"iso_3166_1":"AU","title":"Croatia's Coast","type":""}]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":233964,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Nicholas Ofczarek","